"Below the search box you can see a list of key bindings, &ie; associations "
"between actions (&eg; Copy) shown in the <guilabel>Action</guilabel> column "
"and keys or combination of keys (&eg; <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>C</keycap> </keycombo>) shown in the <guilabel>Shortcut</guilabel> "
"or <guilabel>Alternate</guilabel> column."
msgstr ""

